I have done the first 2 parts and I am half way through the 3rd and I am finding some of the information to be inaccurate.   According to the NHS in the UK condom failure rate is 2%,  not 15% as stated in this course.  It also seems to put a bit too much emphasis on Abstinence.   I would recommend every one taking this course to do some further research into contraception and find out more accurate information.
